text: Calyptranthes densiflora is a species of tree in the family Myrtaceae. It is endemic to Peru. It is listed as vulnerable by the IUCN. It has simple, broad leaves. It is a photoautotroph. ==References== Category:Endemic flora of Peru densiflora Category:Data deficient plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by Eduard Friedrich Poeppig
